Package: basefwx
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Depends:
 libbasefwx3 (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: BaseFWX command-line cryptographic codec tool
 BaseFWX is a cryptographic codec toolkit for files, byte streams, and
 selected media carrier formats.
 .
 This package contains the BaseFWX command-line tool. The shared runtime
 library is kept in libbasefwx3 so applications can link against the same
 packaged implementation instead of bundling a private copy.

Package: libbasefwx3
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: BaseFWX C++ cryptographic codec library (runtime)
 BaseFWX is a C++ library implementing the FixCraft cryptographic codec
 format, including AES-based encryption, Argon2id key derivation, and
 ML-KEM-768 post-quantum key encapsulation.
 .
 This package contains the shared library required to run programs
 linked against libbasefwx. ML-KEM-768 support is enabled by the build
 through the packaged liboqs dependency rather than a vendored static copy.

Package: libbasefwx-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 libbasefwx3 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libssl-dev,
 zlib1g-dev,
 liblzma-dev,
 libargon2-dev,
 liboqs-dev,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: BaseFWX C++ cryptographic codec library (development files)
 BaseFWX is a C++ library implementing the FixCraft cryptographic codec
 format, including AES-based encryption, Argon2id key derivation, and
 ML-KEM-768 post-quantum key encapsulation.
 .
 This package contains the headers, the CMake package config, and the
 pkg-config file needed to build software against libbasefwx.
